{"id":1522,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":270,"title":"Conversation 140","subtitle":"Checking a Purchase Requisition","level":"B1","parts":14,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-140.1522/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/0-conversation-140.mp3","transcript":"Hey, Ian, are you logged in to the system right now?\nYeah, why are you asking?\nWell, my computer crashed unexpectedly half an hour ago,\nso I can't check my email.\nCan I borrow yours for a second?\nBut company computers do not allow us to switch users.\nRight, I forgot.\nCould you check my inbox for me then?\nI'd like to know if the product development department has submitted its purchase requisition.\nSure, hold on...\nThere it is.\nDo you want me to print it out for you?\nThat would be great. Thanks!\nI just need a copy of this purchase requisition form.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:02:02","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hey, Ian, are you logged in to the system right now?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":3.99},{"position":2,"content":"Yeah, why are you asking?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/2.mp3","time_start":4.95,"time_end":7.0},{"position":3,"content":"Well, my computer crashed unexpectedly half an hour ago,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/3.mp3","time_start":7.54,"time_end":11.45},{"position":4,"content":"so I can't check my email.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/4.mp3","time_start":11.45,"time_end":13.42},{"position":5,"content":"Can I borrow yours for a second?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/5.mp3","time_start":13.8,"time_end":15.89},{"position":6,"content":"But company computers do not allow us to switch users.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/6.mp3","time_start":16.62,"time_end":20.75},{"position":7,"content":"Right, I forgot.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/7.mp3","time_start":21.17,"time_end":22.98},{"position":8,"content":"Could you check my inbox for me then?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/8.mp3","time_start":22.98,"time_end":25.41},{"position":9,"content":"I'd like to know if the product development department has submitted its purchase requisition.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/9.mp3","time_start":25.59,"time_end":30.36},{"position":10,"content":"Sure, hold on...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/10.mp3","time_start":31.05,"time_end":32.47},{"position":11,"content":"There it is.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/11.mp3","time_start":32.84,"time_end":33.93},{"position":12,"content":"Do you want me to print it out for you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/12.mp3","time_start":34.3,"time_end":36.36},{"position":13,"content":"That would be great. Thanks!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/13.mp3","time_start":37.08,"time_end":39.33},{"position":14,"content":"I just need a copy of this purchase requisition form.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-140-2024-09-14-18-18-30/14.mp3","time_start":39.33,"time_end":42.59}]}